    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. can u go into more detail about specific landmark cases that show how this doctrine has been a win for civil rights? i want to give them some concrete examples of when the court used substantive due process to basically stop the government from trampling on people's essential freedoms.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
